title: Sample Book, Book No. 11, 1948
description: 168 pages of 40 different sidewall and border designs. Includes "In Line" and "Ducks and Grasses" by Ilonka Karasz.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Book No. 11, 1948; Designed by Ilonka Karasz (American, b. Hungary, 1896-1981); USA; machine printed on paper; Overall: 52 x 53.5 x 5 cm (20 1/2 x 21 1/16 x 1 15/16 in.); Gift of Unknown Donor; 1980-77-1-1/178
